Ellie Mae's Tiki Bar
/$
$
Cape Canaveral's Neighborhood Bar
/$
$
Welcome to Ellie Mae's Tiki Bar, where we offer a unique blend of craft cocktails, fresh food, cold beer and live entertainment. Our neighborhood bar is a great place for people to come and relax, enjoy a drink, and have a great time.
We believe that everyone should have the opportunity to experience the joy of a tiki bar. Our staff is friendly and knowledgeable, and always willing to provide you with the best experience possible. We look forward to seeing you soon!
